programRules.name: Hide time interval type a and chain of events b if report disease or condition directly leading to death not filled
programRules.condition: !d2:hasValue('020-100-MD02a1. Report disease or condition directly leading to death - Cause of death')

programRules.name: Chain of events (b) Hide time interval if time interval type blank
programRules.condition: !d2:hasValue('020-100-MD02a1. Report chain of events in order  time interval type b')

programRules.name: Hide time interval type c and d and chain of events d if chain of events c not filled
programRules.condition: !d2:hasValue('020-100-MD02a2 Report chain of events in order c')

programRules.name: Hide date and reason for surgery if surgery not performed
programRules.condition: #{100-OD01. Was surgery performed within the last 4 weeks} != 'Yes'

programRules.name: Chain of events (c) Hide time interval if time interval type blank
programRules.condition: !d2:hasValue('020-100-MD02a2 Report chain of events in order time interval type c')

programRules.name: Report disease or condition leading to death Hide time interval if time interval type blank
programRules.condition: !d2:hasValue('020-100-MD02a1. Report disease or condition directly leading to death - Cause of death time interval type')

programRules.name: Hide point pregnant, referred from, parity if deceased was not pregnant
programRules.condition: #{100-DP01. For women was the deceased pregnant} != 'Yes'

programRules.name: Hide question if findings were used in certification if autopsy not requested
Chain of events (d) Hide time interval if time interval type blank
programRules.condition: !d2:hasValue('020-100-MD02a2 Report chain of events in order time interval type d')

programRules.name: Hide date of injury, how external cause occured, place of occurance of external cause if death not by external cause
programRules.condition: #{100-MD10j. Manner of death - external cause or poisoning} != '1'

programRules.name: Hide time interval type b and chain of events c if chain of events b not filled
programRules.condition: !d2:hasValue('020-100-MD02a1. Report chain of events in order  b')
